<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kulottuṅkacoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>varkku yā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇṭu <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>7</unclear></hi> vatu nilakaṅkaraiyaru
<lb n="3"/>Ivar paṟṟil nāṭṭār veṭṭai
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kkup pona Iṭattile paḷḷi Uḻuk
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kai nāṭāḻvān paccai paḷḷiyaik
<lb n="6"/>kaippiḻaipā<unclear>ṭe</unclear> yeyya nīlakaṅkarai
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yaru nāṭṭārumiruntu keṭṭu<note n="69-1">The inscription stops here.</note> 
</p>

